description:
Can God trust us with difficult conversations?

In our lives, there will be times when we find ourselves engaged in difficult conversations, and how we handle these conversations can have the power to either bring someone closer to God or push them further away from Him.

This #cut clip from the video, "Relationships [How to Have Tough Conversations without Hurting Others]" https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z_iwmD63PS0&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo8z8roW1briblbYYPS-HpyE&index=20, demonstrates how we can handle difficult conversations. Interaction with others can sometimes be challenging, but if God is within us, He will empower us to use those conversations for His glory.

Watch the video to learn the secret to maintaining loving relationships with others, even through difficult conversations.
